{"name":"Tankard of Plenty","permission":{"default":0,"nxWKrSSCtrgMV99N":3},"flags":{"R20Converter":{"handout-order":14,"handout-archived":false}},"content":"<h4>Tankard of Plenty</h4><em>Wondrous item, unique</em><br><br>Speaking the command word (“Illefarn”) while grasping the handle fills the tankard with three pints of rich dwarven ale. This power can be used up to three times per day.<br>","img":"","_id":"ML2oixzYBQTgOEQN"}
