{"name":"Dagger of Venom","permission":{"default":0,"nxWKrSSCtrgMV99N":3},"flags":{"R20Converter":{"handout-order":5,"handout-archived":false}},"content":"<h4>Dagger of Venom</h4><em>Weapon (dagger), rare</em><br><br>You gain a +1 bonus to attack and damage rolls made with this magic weapon.<br><br>You can use an action to cause thick, black poison to coat the blade. The poison remains for 1 minute or until an attack using this weapon hits a creature. That creature must succeed on a DC 15 Constitution saving throw or take 2d10 poison damage and become poisoned for 1 minute. The dagger can't be used this way again until the next dawn.<br>","img":"worlds/hoard-of-the-dragon-queen/journal/012_-_Magic_Items/005_-_Dagger_of_Venom/avatar_1.png","_id":"VFDZqZV8ZGh6x1yQ"}
