{"name":"Weapon, +1, +2, or +3","permission":{"default":0,"nxWKrSSCtrgMV99N":3},"flags":{"R20Converter":{"handout-order":16,"handout-archived":false}},"content":"<h4>Weapon, +1, +2, or +3</h4><em>Weapon (any). uncommon (+1), rare (+2), or very rare (+3)</em><br><br>You have a bonus to attack and damage rolls made with this magic weapon. The bonus is determined by the weapon's rarity.","img":"","_id":"zFUb5KpRuN4IOWzp"}
